    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has visible damage including dents, scratches, and paint deterioration across multiple panels. The interior shows heavy wear with damaged upholstery and worn surfaces throughout. Mechanically functional but will likely require repairs. Suitable for buyers looking for a project car or basic transportation on a tight budget.",
